overview: Norma Jean wants to go to the elementary school dance Saturday night, but she's worried she won't have a partner. When Travis's friend Seth comes to visit, Norma discovers a partner for the dance...and two girls who want to spoil her fun. But it'll take more than a bad makeover to stop Norma and her new friend from having an unforgettable night.
title: Cabbage Patch Kids: Saturday Night
